It is an intense fight of the arcane magics, aggro is now on casters leaving them with their resists and clerics as only protection. (Note should be taken that the sarnak does not engage the casters in melee..Until it run out of mana perhaps..but it should be a weak melee in that case)<br>
<br>
The tanks break free and goes after the sarnak, to no luck as he yonders away easily.<br>
<br>
The casters begin to severly stun the sarnak giving the tanks opportunity to engage it with their gleaming swords..and sticks..and fists.<br>
<br>
Needless to say the battle is won and the casters win the purple heart <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
